Sinatrails is sinatra bootstrap project to create web application with Rails-like directory structure and Active Record as ORM.

To use this project:
1. gem install sinatra
2. gem install haml
3. gem install activerecord
4. git clone git://github.com/kuntoaji/sinatrails.git
5. run rake db:migrate to create user. Note: Currently only support db:migrate for migration.
6. ./scripts/server to run the server or ./scripts/console to the console.
